## Attribution Requirements

When using this server's visual vocabulary mappings, please cite:

- Court of Master Sommeliers deductive tasting methodology
- WSET (Wine & Spirit Education Trust) systematic approach
- UC Davis Wine Aroma Wheel (A.C. Noble, R.A. Arnold, et al.)

This software translates expert knowledge that belongs to the wine education
community. The categorical structure and implementation are original work,
but the underlying sensory vocabulary is established expert knowledge.
